Learn how to build robust robotic applications using ROS2 (Robot Operating System 2), the next generation of ROS.

## What You'll Learn

- ROS2 fundamentals and architecture
- Creating nodes, topics, and services
- Building custom messages and actions
- Integration with sensors and actuators
- Navigation and planning with Nav2
- Simulation with Gazebo

## Target Audience

- Robotics students and researchers
- Engineers transitioning from ROS1
- Developers interested in autonomous systems

## Projects

- Mobile robot navigation
- Sensor fusion for perception
- Human-robot interaction scenarios

